summary: Adds a back door to Riften, near the Graveyard
descriptionHtml: This is a simple mod that adds another back door to the city of Riften. It is at the wooden panel in the back of the town, near the graveyard. This was made so you don\'t have to go full circle around the city to get to the trail that is already there, leading towards the Blackbriar\'s place, Dawnguard keep, and other things in that general direction.
author: Pan Dragondagger --- aka -  Rex1029
